(118, 45, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"65e4d06\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"container_type\":\"grid\",\"presetTitle\":\"Grid\",\"presetIcon\":\"eicon-container-grid\",\"grid_columns_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":2,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_rows_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"83a53e0\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/s1.jpg\",\"id\":48,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"454be58\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/s2.jpg\",\"id\":47,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"4126ab2\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e9b539d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Pri\\u010da o Smokvici po\\u010dela je tako \\u0161to \\u010detiri prijatelja sanjaju da otvore restoran koji \\u0107e biti omiljeno mesto za okupljanje njihovih prijatelja, porodice i svih koji \\u017eele da \\u0161to \\u010de\\u0161\\u0107e u\\u017eivaju svim svojim \\u010dulima.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#454040\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"b8e03c0\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/s3.jpg\",\"id\":100,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"abafe28\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Danas, sa velikim brojem restorana Smokvica \\u0161irom Beograda, koji su potpuno prilago\\u0111eni sredini u kojoj se nalaze, namere \\u010detvorice prijatelja su uspele.<\\/p><p>Stvoreni su topli, kiseli, kreativni ambijenti provansalskog stila u kojima ljudi razli\\u010ditog uzrasta, zanimanja i potreba mogu prona\\u0107i kutak za sebe. Na\\u0161i gosti su ljudi koji \\u017eele dobru kafu, limunadu sa sve\\u017eom mentom i opu\\u0161tanje u ba\\u0161ti, oni koji vole bogat, \\u0161aren i uzbudljiv doru\\u010dak, oni koji su na posao do\\u0161li dok polako pijuckaju \\u010daj, ali vole i ukusan obrok koji ne mo\\u017ee na\\u0107i bilo gde drugde.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#454040\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"79ad8b0\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"container_type\":\"grid\",\"presetTitle\":\"Grid\",\"presetIcon\":\"eicon-container-grid\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"grid_columns_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":2,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_rows_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_justify_items\":\"center\",\"grid_align_items\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"90cbbbd\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/s5.jpg\",\"id\":99,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"24be018\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/s4.jpg\",\"id\":101,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"a2967bd\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Svako od Smokvica vo\\u0111en je entuzijazmom da se bogato nasle\\u0111e gastronomskih i estetskih do\\u017eivljaja najbolje prenese, jer je velika umetnost pru\\u017eiti \\u010doveku iskustvo za sva \\u010dula.<\\/p><p>\\u201ePravi zanatlija najbolje odre\\u0111uje kreativni impuls i kontinuiranu potragu za jedinstveno\\u0161\\u0107u u dizajnu i izrazu.\\u201d<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#454040\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"7832b4e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Jedan od Smokvica restorana mo\\u017eete prona\\u0107i i na ovoj adresi!<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#454040\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"f4a9efa\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"address\":\"Gospodar Jovanova 45\",\"zoom\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":15,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"google_maps\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
