(165, 56, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"b880ad0\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"container_type\":\"grid\",\"presetTitle\":\"Grid\",\"presetIcon\":\"eicon-container-grid\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":96.774},\"grid_columns_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":2,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_rows_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_justify_items\":\"center\",\"grid_align_items\":\"center\",\"_flex_size\":\"none\",\"_element_width\":\"initial\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"994a2f5\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/j1.jpg\",\"id\":59,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"6d2a743\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/j2.jpg\",\"id\":58,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"b05667d\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"210b80d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Na mestu gde je svojevremeno bio sme\\u0161ten prvi no\\u0107ni klub na Balkanu \\u2013 Diskoteka kog Laze, nedavno je otvoren jedinstveni klub Jet Set koji se izdvaja kako po savr\\u0161enom enterijeru tako i po izboru jela i pi\\u0107a, ali i odli\\u010dnom muzi\\u010dkom programu i stalnim gostovanjima razli\\u010ditih DJ-eva.<\\/p><p>Mesto je, ina\\u010de, inspirisano no\\u0107nim \\u017eivotom Pariza tokom 20-tih godina pro\\u0161log veka, kada su u ovom gradu \\u017eiveli Koko \\u0160anel, Igor Stravinski, Klod Mone, Zelda Ficd\\u017eerald\\u2026<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#464343\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"935e36a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/j3.jpg\",\"id\":109,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"c91c2c4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Zahvaljuju\\u0107i elegantnom enterijeru, koji podse\\u0107a na pozori\\u0161nu scenu, prigu\\u0161enom osvetljenju i muzici DJ-a, koja se lagano \\u010duje u pozadini, ovo mesto je savr\\u0161eno za izlazak, ali i predstavlja pravi gastro u\\u017eitak.\\u00a0Meni je osmislio \\u0161ef kuhinje Andrej Balahnov, a sastoji se od vrhunskih jela poput gove\\u0111eg tartar bifteka ili peruanskog\\u00a0sevi\\u010dea koji se pravi pred vama. Pored toga, na ovoj adresi slu\\u017ee se i mo\\u017eda najbolji kokteli u gradu.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#464343\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"fdd0bb1\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/j4.webp\",\"id\":108,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"e7a4813\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"address\":\"Svetogorska, 17, Belgrade, Serbia 11000\",\"zoom\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":15,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"google_maps\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
