(225, 72, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"e81bf00\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"container_type\":\"grid\",\"presetTitle\":\"Grid\",\"presetIcon\":\"eicon-container-grid\",\"grid_columns_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":2,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_rows_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_justify_items\":\"center\",\"grid_align_items\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"5988ac0\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/l2.jpg\",\"id\":74,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"22c4fb5\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/l3.jpg\",\"id\":76,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"image_size\":\"medium_large\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"712d4da\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"bb8c070\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Postoje mesta koja su ispunjena posebnom atmosferom, energijom i toplinom; mesta u kojima nas do\\u010deka iskren osmeh i u kojima strast, posve\\u0107enost i ukus prepoznajemo u svakom detalju. Njih volimo i njima se vra\\u0107amo jer \\u010dine da se ose\\u0107amo prijatno i slobodno kao kod svoje ku\\u0107e. Jedno od takvih mesta je upravo\\u00a0<strong>La Casa de Caffe<\\/strong>\\u00a0koje privla\\u010di svojim mediteranskim \\u0161armom i akusti\\u010dnom atmosferom. Sti\\u010de se ose\\u0107aj kao da ste na nekoj udaljenoj morskoj destinaciji. Luksuzan ambijent krase prirodni materijali i udoban name\\u0161taj koji nije svakida\\u0161nji.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#4D4A4A\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"fea5684\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/l4.jpg\",\"id\":127,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"17b1a32\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<div class=\\\"elementor-element elementor-element-55981e9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\\\" data-id=\\\"55981e9\\\" data-element_type=\\\"widget\\\" data-widget_type=\\\"text-editor.default\\\"><div class=\\\"elementor-widget-container\\\"><p>Iskusni i srda\\u010dni baristi u La Casa De Caffe predstavi\\u0107e kafe iz tri razli\\u010dite dr\\u017eave.\\u00a0<strong>Sorta kafe iz Brazil<\\/strong>a koja je 2021. odlikovana kao najbolja a krase je ukusi \\u010dokolade i pralina. Dok\\u00a0<strong>kafe iz Kolumbije i Etiopije<\\/strong>\\u00a0dolaze sa manjih planta\\u017ea i predstavljaju pravu eksluzivu po karakteristikama. Stavka koja \\u010dini sve kafe i \\u010dajeve jo\\u0161 kvalitetnijim je voda. Revolucionarna filtracija reverznom-osmozom doprinosi ukusu i bistrini u \\u0161oljici.\\u00a0<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><div class=\\\"elementor-element elementor-element-37889c2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\\\" data-id=\\\"37889c2\\\" data-element_type=\\\"widget\\\" data-widget_type=\\\"text-editor.default\\\"><div class=\\\"elementor-widget-container\\\"><p>Pored kvalitetnog espresa, u ponudi se nalaze ru\\u010dno pripremljene filter kafe. \\u0160ank je osmi\\u0161ljen kao pozornica, a jedinstveni Brew Bar je iskustvo za sebe. Svaki gost je u mogu\\u0107nosti da se pridru\\u017ei baristima tokom pripreme i pro\\u0161iri svoju perspektivu na ovu temu.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div>\",\"text_color\":\"#4D4A4A\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"a32e5bc\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"container_type\":\"grid\",\"presetTitle\":\"Grid\",\"presetIcon\":\"eicon-container-grid\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"grid_columns_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":2,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_rows_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_justify_items\":\"center\",\"grid_align_items\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8349b8a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/l5.jpg\",\"id\":125,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"430cd1b\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/l6.jpg\",\"id\":126,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"a694757\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"container_type\":\"grid\",\"presetTitle\":\"Grid\",\"presetIcon\":\"eicon-container-grid\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"grid_columns_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":2,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_rows_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"73091df\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Trenutak kada Sunce zalazi vreme je da se sa kratkog espresa pre\\u0111e na druga kratka pi\\u0107a.\\u00a0<strong>Obo\\u017eavaoci ruma<\\/strong>\\u00a0se na trenutak mogu prona\\u0107i u Gvatemali uz Ron Zacapu, koji nastaje me\\u0161avinom rumova starih od 6 do 23 godine ili pak u Venecueli uz Diplomatico Reserve, 12 godina starog ruma. Dve vrste d\\u017eina upotpunjuju u\\u017eitak. Young Salt, d\\u017ein doma\\u0107e proizvodnje i d\\u017ein iz \\u0160kotske po imenu Botanist.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#4D4A4A\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"1a09399\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p><strong>U ponudi se nalaze i eskluzive kao \\u0161to su Nikka Days, Glenmorangie Quinta Ruban 14 godina star visk<\\/strong>i. Sa\\u017eet, jednostavan ali neophodan izbor koktela poput Cold Brew D\\u017ein Tonika, Negronija, Huga, Mohita, kreirani su od strane izuzetnih ljudi sa najboljim sastojcima koje jedan premium lokal mo\\u017ee da ponudi. Pritom nisu izuzeti ni obo\\u017eavatelji likera koji mogu u\\u017eivati i degusitrati Amareto Disaronno ili Meukow Xpresso Cafe &amp; Cognac.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#4D4A4A\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"3f8e5b5\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Na najluksuznijoj lokaciji u gradu!<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#4D4A4A\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"59470f3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"address\":\"Bulevar Vudroa Vilsona 8, Beograd\",\"zoom\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":15,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"google_maps\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
