(353, 106, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"f36f11e\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"82f527d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"title\":\"Privremeno zatvoren!?!?\",\"header_size\":\"h3\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#454748\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"1a1e881\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Na\\u017ealost... istina je to \\u0161to \\u010dujete. Luksuzan i sofisticirani lokal Jet Set je privremeno zatvoren usled renoviranja.<\\/p><p>Datum ponovnog otvaranja nam jo\\u0161 uvek nije poznat, ali verujemo da kada se vrate na scenu, bi\\u0107e najpo\\u017eeljnije mesto za izlazak u celom Beogradu!<\\/p><p>Nestrpljivo i\\u0161\\u010dekujemo taj trenutak... ;)<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#4F4A4A\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d73d62e\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"83b5d8e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/j5.jpg\",\"id\":257,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
