(390, 121, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"f169de1\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"acdee1d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p class=\\\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"color_18 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"wixui-rich-text__text\\\">Da je \\u017eivot u Beogradu jedna velika \\u017eurka, Angry Monk bi bio najnovija, najzabavnija \\u017eurka u gradu.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"color_18 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"wixui-rich-text__text\\\">Prostor je ure\\u0111en u duhu \\\"ku\\u0107ne varijante\\\" gde dominira duga\\u010dak bar iza kojeg kuvari prikazuju svoje ume\\u0107e.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#454242\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"21ec856\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d9f74ce\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/a3.jpeg\",\"id\":116,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"484e0a7\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"554075a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p class=\\\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"color_18 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"wixui-rich-text__text\\\">Druga\\u010dije od tipi\\u010dnog su\\u0161i mesta, Angry Monk nudi hranu inspirisanu Japanom i Azijom.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"color_18 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"wixui-rich-text__text\\\">Meni poseduje jela koja su rezultat dugog i detaljnog procesa u\\u010denja u zemlji izlaze\\u0107eg sunca kombinovane sa lokalnim sastojcima.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"color_18 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"wixui-rich-text__text\\\">Dizajn restorana je inspirisan velikim gradovima poput Tokija i Kjota.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#454242\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"49f3d9a\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"container_type\":\"grid\",\"presetTitle\":\"Grid\",\"presetIcon\":\"eicon-container-grid\",\"grid_columns_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":2,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_rows_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_justify_items\":\"center\",\"grid_align_items\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"6f07868\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/a4.avif\",\"id\":118,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"ec78873\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/a5.webp\",\"id\":117,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1f7cf41\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e9b203f\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p class=\\\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"color_18 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"wixui-rich-text__text\\\">Uz duga\\u010dak bar koji dominira prostorom, Angry Monk predstavlja kulminaciju raznovrsnosti koktela i gostoprimstva u Beogradu.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"color_18 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"wixui-rich-text__text\\\">Sa neverovatnim dekorom i inovativnim menijem pi\\u0107a, Angry Monk je zaista najnezaboravnije i najupe\\u010datljivije iskustvo \\u0161to se ti\\u010de barova u Beogradu<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#454242\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
