(624, 161, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"0049d65\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"container_type\":\"grid\",\"presetTitle\":\"Grid\",\"presetIcon\":\"eicon-container-grid\",\"grid_columns_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":2,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_rows_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_justify_items\":\"center\",\"grid_align_items\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2a784ff\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/a2.png\",\"id\":67,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"6987cba\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/a1.jpg\",\"id\":66,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1315380\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f619cad\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p class=\\\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"color_18 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"wixui-rich-text__text\\\">Da je \\u017eivot u Beogradu jedna velika \\u017eurka, Angry Monk bi bio najnovija, najzabavnija \\u017eurka u gradu.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"color_18 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"wixui-rich-text__text\\\">Prostor je ure\\u0111en u duhu \\u201cku\\u0107ne varijante\\u201d gde dominira duga\\u010dak bar iza kojeg kuvari prikazuju svoje ume\\u0107e.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#464343\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"f95b8bd\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/a3.jpeg\",\"id\":116,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"3ae5887\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p class=\\\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"color_18 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"wixui-rich-text__text\\\">Druga\\u010dije od tipi\\u010dnog su\\u0161i mesta, Angry Monk nudi hranu inspirisanu Japanom i Azijom.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"color_18 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"wixui-rich-text__text\\\">Meni poseduje jela koja su rezultat dugog i detaljnog procesa u\\u010denja u zemlji izlaze\\u0107eg sunca kombinovane sa lokalnim sastojcima.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"color_18 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"wixui-rich-text__text\\\">Dizajn restorana je inspirisan velikim gradovima poput Tokija i Kjota.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#464343\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"2384c9a\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"container_type\":\"grid\",\"presetTitle\":\"Grid\",\"presetIcon\":\"eicon-container-grid\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"grid_columns_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":2,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_rows_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_justify_items\":\"center\",\"grid_align_items\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"83deb55\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/a4.avif\",\"id\":118,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"15e3a18\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/a5.webp\",\"id\":117,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"296fc3b\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p class=\\\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"color_18 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"wixui-rich-text__text\\\">Uz duga\\u010dak bar koji dominira prostorom, Angry Monk predstavlja kulminaciju raznovrsnosti koktela i gostoprimstva u Beogradu.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p class=\\\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"color_18 wixui-rich-text__text\\\"><span class=\\\"wixui-rich-text__text\\\">Sa neverovatnim dekorom i inovativnim menijem pi\\u0107a, Angry Monk je zaista najnezaboravnije i najupe\\u010datljivije iskustvo \\u0161to se ti\\u010de barova u Beogradu.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#464343\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"dbf85f8\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Mo\\u017eete ga prona\\u0107i na slede\\u0107oj lokaciji!<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#464343\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"be08f86\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"address\":\"Uzun Mirkova 11, Beograd 11000\",\"zoom\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":15,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"google_maps\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
