(674, 167, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"174baed\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"container_type\":\"grid\",\"presetTitle\":\"Grid\",\"presetIcon\":\"eicon-container-grid\",\"grid_columns_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":2,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_rows_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_justify_items\":\"center\",\"grid_align_items\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b879754\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/v2.webp\",\"id\":83,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"f33b03e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/v1.jpg\",\"id\":84,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"4349d9a\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f23f664\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Villa Maska je jedna od onih destinacija u Beogradu koja o\\u010darava na prvi pogled i ostavlja trajan utisak na svakog posetioca. Sme\\u0161tena u mirnom delu grada, ova prelepa vila sa svojim jedinstvenim ambijentom pru\\u017ea ose\\u0107aj kao da ste zakora\\u010dili u svet magije i elegancije.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#403C3C\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"29d9b75\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/v5.jpg\",\"id\":137,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"d6ff718\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Kada kro\\u010dite kroz kapiju Villa Maske, do\\u010deka\\u0107e vas pa\\u017eljivo ure\\u0111en eksterijer sa bujnim zelenilom i cve\\u0107em koje krasi svako \\u0107o\\u0161e dvori\\u0161ta. Sama vila odi\\u0161e starinskim \\u0161armom, dok vas unutra\\u0161nji prostor uvodi u svet umetnosti i luksuza. Zidovi su ukra\\u0161eni slikama, skulpturama i drugim umetni\\u010dkim delima, dok su svetla prigu\\u0161ena, stvaraju\\u0107i intimnu atmosferu savr\\u0161enu za ve\\u010deru udvoje ili opu\\u0161teni obrok sa prijateljima.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#403C3C\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"dfffeae\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"container_type\":\"grid\",\"presetTitle\":\"Grid\",\"presetIcon\":\"eicon-container-grid\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"grid_columns_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":2,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_rows_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_justify_items\":\"center\",\"grid_align_items\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3a6b3cf\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/v6.jpg\",\"id\":138,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"0d7fa29\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/v3.jpg\",\"id\":139,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"a5e9f2e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Meni Villa Maske je prava poslastica za sva \\u010dula. Restoran nudi raznovrsnu ponudu jela koja kombinuju najbolje od me\\u0111unarodne kuhinje sa posebnim naglaskom na mediteranska i balkanska jela. Svako jelo je pa\\u017eljivo pripremljeno od najkvalitetnijih sastojaka i servirano sa stilom. Mo\\u017eete u\\u017eivati u sve\\u017eim morskim plodovima, so\\u010dnim mesnim specijalitetima, kao i vegetarijanskim opcijama koje \\u0107e zadovoljiti i najprobirljivije gurmane.<\\/p><p>Pi\\u0107a i vina u Villa Maski su pri\\u010da za sebe. Restoran posve\\u0107uje posebnu pa\\u017enju svom vinskom podrumu, nude\\u0107i \\u0161irok izbor doma\\u0107ih i stranih vina koja savr\\u0161eno komplimentiraju jelima iz menija. Stru\\u010dni somelijeri su tu da vam pomognu u odabiru savr\\u0161enog vina koje \\u0107e upotpuniti va\\u0161 obrok.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#403C3C\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"c071570\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/v4.webp\",\"id\":140,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"865f34c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Potra\\u017eite ga na mapi!<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#403C3C\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"888e1cb\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"address\":\"Rankeova 7, Beograd 11000\",\"zoom\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":15,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"google_maps\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
