(1162, 234, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"ab3ee63\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"20ab85a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"title\":\"Dizajn koji obara sa nogu!\",\"header_size\":\"h3\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#4A4D4F\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"87ebc51\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/v5.jpg\",\"id\":137,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"6fc3d9f\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Pro\\u0161log veka, u ovo vreme, lokal Villa Maska nije izgledao ovako. Renovirana je u lokal koji vas sigurno ne\\u0107e ostaviti ravnodu\\u0161nim! Atmosfera odi\\u0161e egzotikom sa Dalekog Istoka i starinskim komadima name\\u0161taja na\\u0161ih baka, sve to ukomponovano do detalja nepogre\\u0161ivim ukusom samih vlasnika.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#464343\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d435fef\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"container_type\":\"grid\",\"presetTitle\":\"Grid\",\"presetIcon\":\"eicon-container-grid\",\"grid_columns_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":2,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_rows_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_justify_items\":\"center\",\"grid_align_items\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"72ceb88\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/v3.jpg\",\"id\":139,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"763ffb7\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/v6.jpg\",\"id\":138,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"a7b6c63\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"fe0980c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Preneo je duh starog: ure\\u0111en je kao da je nekoliko istra\\u017eiva\\u010da Afrike i Dalekog istoka donelo sve svoje ukrasne predmete: koplja, maske, totemske statuete i ostavilo ih kao ukras u restoranu. Vili u koju se uselila \\u201cMaska\\u201d probijene su eta\\u017ee, tako da se dobio niz veoma atraktivnih galerija odakle mo\\u017ee da se vidi \\u0161ank.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#433F3F\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"f3b4373\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e62c9d0\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/v4.webp\",\"id\":140,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
