(1253, 250, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"ed17bca\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a08ab6c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"title\":\"Panja, paznja! Spremaju Vam se top ponude!\",\"header_size\":\"h3\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#494E51\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"ed5e1a9\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/l7.jpg\",\"id\":244,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":86,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"ac731f8\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Postoje mesta koja odi\\u0161u posebnom atmosferom, energijom i toplinom. Mesta u kojima nas uvek do\\u010deka iskren osmeh i u kojima strast, posve\\u0107enost i ukus prepoznajemo u svakom detalju. Njih volimo i njima se vra\\u0107amo jer \\u010dine da se ose\\u0107amo prijatno i potpuno slobodno.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#453F3F\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"ecc96aa\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"container_type\":\"grid\",\"presetTitle\":\"Grid\",\"presetIcon\":\"eicon-container-grid\",\"grid_columns_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":2,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_rows_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_justify_items\":\"center\",\"grid_align_items\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9d4a986\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/l1.webp\",\"id\":75,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"ed3caf9\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/l8.jpg\",\"id\":243,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":86,\"sizes\":[]},\"height\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":305,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"f6cd095\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"container_type\":\"grid\",\"presetTitle\":\"Grid\",\"presetIcon\":\"eicon-container-grid\",\"grid_columns_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":2,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_rows_grid\":{\"unit\":\"fr\",\"size\":1,\"sizes\":[]},\"grid_justify_items\":\"center\",\"grid_align_items\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c91a00c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Eksluzivan izbor vina sa najboljih planta\\u017ea sveta, kao i nesvakida\\u0161nja ponuda destilata. U\\u017eiva\\u0107ete u malim ritualima, spoju sve\\u017eih i egzoti\\u010dnih ukusa i u jedinstvenom ambijentu u jednom od najuzbudljivijih delova grada.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#454040\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"fed3afc\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Toliko razli\\u010ditih sorta kafe, izbor \\u0107e Vam biti trostruko ote\\u017ean! Od afri\\u010dkog blenda, do sorti iz Kolumbije i Etiopije...\\u00a0<\\/p><p>Za\\u010dinite svoju kafu dodacima sa aromom \\u010dokolade, pralina i mnogih drugih.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#403C3C\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
