(1519, 287, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"f3fc2b6\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7ccb5f3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"title\":\"Doga\\u0111aji i ponude\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#494C4D\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"563c08b\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>U ponudi ovog\\u00a0kafi\\u0107a\\u00a0u\\u00a0Beogradu\\u00a0se nalazi\\u00a0<b>standardni asortiman<\\/b>\\u00a0alkoholnih i bezalkoholnih pi\\u0107a i kafa, ali je usluga vi\\u0161e orijentisana na\\u00a0<b>pripremu koktela<\\/b>.<\\/p><p>Ono \\u0161to kafi\\u0107 Blaznavac \\u010dini specifi\\u010dnim jesu tzv. \\u2018<b>litarski kokteli<\\/b>\\u2019 koji se slu\\u017ee u bokalima i idealni su za grupne izlaske, i preporu\\u010dujemo koktel pod nazivom\\u00a0<b>Zombie<\\/b>\\u00a0koji je za ljubitelje malo ja\\u010deg ukusa.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#4F4949\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"c1621d4\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"fd12617\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/b5.jpg\",\"id\":270,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":68,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"01afc13\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4009e05\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p>Ako ste zainteresovani za kupovinu slika, u ovom kafi\\u0107u \\u010desto se sprovode\\u00a0<b>prodajne izlo\\u017ebe<\\/b>\\u00a0kako slika, tako i crte\\u017ea, grafika, fotografija, rukotvorina, keramike\\u2026<\\/p><p>Tako\\u0111e, deo uobi\\u010dajenih doga\\u0111aja u kafi\\u0107u Blaznavac su\\u00a0<b>muzi\\u010dki nastupi \\u00a0<\\/b>ali\\u00a0<b>i nastupi stand-up komi\\u010dara<\\/b>.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#4F4949\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"142871f\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4c8f920\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/07\\/b6.jpg\",\"id\":269,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":65,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
